data.description: One of a kind view lot in Riebli area. Super private and surrounded by multi-million dollar properties at this cul-de-sac. The private driveway welcomes you to an expansive usable acre with old foundation from the prior 11000 sf house, BBQ area right next to the pool. The sellers have prepared this lot for new construction. Don't miss this wonderful property, come and build your dream home !
